# Data Migration API Tests

### Get Countries List
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/countries/
Content-Type: application/json


### Create Customer (Admin Endpoint)
POST http://localhost:8000/api-admin/customer-create/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Jane Smith",
    "street1": "456 Oak Avenue",
    "street2": "",  
    "city": "Los Angeles",
    "region": "CA",
    "country": 1,
    "phone": "+1987654321",
    "created_by": "admin",
    "active": true
}

### Create User (Admin Endpoint)
POST http://localhost:8000/api-admin/api-create-user/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "john.doe@example.com",
    "first_name": "John",
    "last_name": "Doe",
    "cust_id": "C00001",
    "created_by": "admin"
}

### Get Sources List
GET http://localhost:8000/api/sources/
Content-Type: application/json

### Test Source Connection - Valid Request
POST http://localhost:8000/api/sources-connection/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "logged_in_user": "3",
    "source_name": "Test Database",
    "hostname": "localhost",
    "port": 5432,
    "user": "testuser",
    "password": "testpassword"

}

###
GET http://localhost:8000/api/api-customer/C00001/sources/


### Test Source Edit API - Sql Server db
GET http://localhost:8000/api/api-customer/C00001/sources/Sql%20Server%20db/edit/
Content-Type: application/json

###
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/customer/C00001/sources/Sql%20Server%20db/edit/

### Test Destination Connection - Single Container
POST http://localhost:8000/api/destinations-connection/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "customer": "C00001",
    "destination_name": "Single Container Destination",
    "hostname": "destination.example.com",
    "instance_number": 1,
    "mode": "single_container"
}

### Test Destination Connection - Multiple Containers with Tenant Database
POST http://localhost:8000/api/destinations-connection/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "customer": "C00001",
    "destination_name": "Multiple Containers - Tenant DB",
    "hostname": "tenant.example.com",
    "instance_number": 2,
    "mode": "multiple_containers",
    "database_type": "tenant_database",
    "tenant_db_name": "tenant_db_001"
}

### Test Destination Connection - Multiple Containers with System Database
POST http://localhost:8000/api/destinations-connection/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "customer": "C00001",
    "destination_name": "Multiple Containers - System DB",
    "hostname": "system.example.com",
    "instance_number": 3,
    "mode": "multiple_containers",
    "database_type": "system_database",
    "system_db_name": "system_db_001"
}

### Test File Upload Preview (with Primary Key)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/file-upload-preview/
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test_data.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

name,email,phone
John Doe,john@example.com,1234567890
Jane Smith,jane@example.com,0987654321
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="user_id"

admin@example.com
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Test File Upload Create Table (with Primary Key)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/write-table/
